General.Name: Lode Resources Ltd
General.Description: Lode Resources Ltd engages in exploring gold, silver, and copper deposits. It holds 100% interests in seven exploration licenses located in the New England Fold Belt in northern New South Wales. The company was incorporated in 2019 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
